data.description: Wow, wow, wow! The sellers are offering a $1000.00 credit for carpets. Come see this beautifully maintained home in the heart of the Northeast Section of the the city. This home has been so well maintained by the sellers, that new buyers will feel right at home. Just pack your bags and move in. When you walk up to your new  home you will find a private outside front patio, for outside gatherings. This home offers 3 over sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Enter into your bright living room with tons of natural light from the large bay window, and relax by the fireplace on those cold winter nights. Enjoy the open concept, updated gourmet kitchen and dining room that offers tons of cabinet space and plenty of room to prepare meals. Catch the game in the downstairs family room that offers a  full bathroom and a walkout basement. This home offers many updates that most homes in the city do not, just to start, off street parking with a back driveway, basement laundry, finished basement, new laminate flooring on the main level, multiple full bathrooms and upgrades galore. Make this home yours today.
